text: Early Saturday upload! The previous Kikuta upload made me look him up to see what he was up to. In doing so, I found his YouTube and Bandcamp pages. This is a free album he released made of various tracks he composed and they're all very game-like, so I suspect they were VGMs that didn't make the cut. This track and its bass is pure Kikuta goodness. There are quite a few tracks in the album that could fit right in Secret of Mana 1&2.
